\c 31
\s Izeluleko inkosi ezinikwa ngunina
\p
\v 1 Amazwi kaLemuweli\x + 31.4. 10.1. Nani 3.24.\x* inkosi yeMasa, unina amfundisa wona\x + 30.1.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Ini, ndodana yami\x + Hlab. 2.12.\x*! Ini-ke, ndodana yesizalo sami\x + Hlab. 2.12.\x*\x + Isa. 49.15.\x*! Ini-ke, ndodana yezithembiso zami\x + 1 Sam. 1.11.\x*\x + Hlab. 2.12.\x*!
\v 3 Unganiki amandla akho kwabesifazana\x + 5.9.\x*, kumbe izindlela zakho ekubhubhiseni amakhosi\x + 7.26. Dute. 17.17. 1 Kho. 11.1.\x*.
\v 4 Kakusikwamakhosi\x + Tshu. 10.17.\x*, Lemuweli\x + 31.4. 10.1. Nani 3.24.\x*, kakusikwamakhosi ukunatha iwayini\x + Hos. 4.11.\x*, kumbe okweziphathamandla ukuloyisa okunathwayo okulamandla\x + 8.15. Hlu. 5.3.\x*.
\v 5 Hlezi anathe, akhohlwe isimiso, aguqule isahlulelo sawo wonke amadodana enhlupheko.
\v 6 Phana okunathwayo okulamandla\x + Hlab. 104.15.\x* kobhubhayo, lewayini kwabababayo emphefumulweni\x + Jobe 29.13.\x*.
\v 7 Kanathe, akhohlwe ubuyanga bakhe, angabe esakhumbula usizi lwakhe.
\v 8 Vulela isimungulu umlomo wakho, udaba lwabo bonke abamiselwe incithakalo\x + Jobe 29.12,15,16. Isa. 1.17.\x*.
\v 9 Vula umlomo wakho, wahlulele ngokulunga\x + Levi 19.15. Dute. 1.16.\x*, umele ilungelo\x + Jobe 29.12,15,16. Isa. 1.17.\x*\x + Jer. 22.16.\x* lomyanga loswelayo\x + 31.20. Hlab. 86.1.\x*.
\s Umfazi olungileyo
\p
\v 10 Ngubani ongathola\x + 20.6.\x* umfazi okhuthela okulungileyo\x + 12.4. 18.22. Ruthe 3.11.\x*? Ngoba intengo yakhe iyedlula kakhulu amatshe amahle\x + Jobe 28.18.\x*.
\v 11 Inhliziyo yomkakhe ithemba kuye, ukuze angasweli impango.
\v 12 Umenzela okuhle, hatshi okubi, insuku zonke zempilo yakhe.
\v 13 Udinga uboya bezimvu lefilakisi, asebenze ngenjabulo yezandla zakhe\x + 31.21,22,24.\x*.
\v 14 Ufanana lemikhumbi yomthengisi; uletha ukudla kwakhe kuvela khatshana.
\v 15 Uvuka kusesebusuku\x + 20.13.\x*, anike indlu yakhe ukudla\x + Luka 12.42. Hlab. 111.5.\x*, lesabelo kuzincekukazi zakhe\x + 30.8.\x*.
\v 16 Anakane ngensimu ayizuze; ngesithelo sezandla zakhe ahlanyele ivini\x + Luka 14.18.\x*.
\v 17 Uyabhinca ukhalo lwakhe\x + 1 Kho. 18.46.\x* ngamandla, aqinise ingalo zakhe\x + 31.17.\x*.
\v 18 Uyananzelela ukuthi ukuthengisa kwakhe kuhle; isibane sakhe kasicitshi ebusuku\x + 13.9.\x*.
\v 19 Welulela izandla zakhe kuluthi lokuphotha, lezandla zakhe zibambe isigodo esilezintambo\x + 2 Sam. 3.29.\x*.
\v 20 Welulela umyanga\x + 31.9.\x* isandla sakhe\x + Roma 12.13.\x*, elulele izandla zakhe koswelayo\x + 31.9.\x*.
\v 21 Kesabi iliqhwa elikhithikileyo ngenxa yabendlu yakhe, ngoba bonke abendlu yakhe bagqokiswe okubomvu\x + 2 Sam. 1.24.\x*.
\v 22 Uzenzela izembeso\x + 7.16.\x*; isigqoko sakhe sililembu elicolekileyo\x + Gen. 41.42. Isam. 19.8,14.\x* leliyibubende\x + Hlu. 8.26.\x*.
\v 23 Umkakhe\x + 12.4.\x* uyaziwa emasangweni\x + Ruthe 3.11. 4.1,2.\x*, lapho ehlezi labadala belizwe\x + Ruthe 3.11. 4.1,2.\x*.
\v 24 Wenza ilembu elicolekileyo kakhulu, alithengise\x + Hlu. 14.12.\x*; anike umthengi ibhanti\x + Jobe 41.6.\x*.
\v 25 Amandla lodumo kuyisigqoko sakhe\x + 31.17.\x*; uyahleka mayelana losuku olulandelayo\x + 8.30,31.\x*.
\v 26 Uvula umlomo wakhe ngenhlakanipho; lemfundiso yomusa iselimini lwakhe.
\v 27 Uqaphela inhambo zomuzi wakhe; kadli isinkwa sobuvila.
\v 28 Abantwana bakhe bayavuka bathi ubusisiwe, \add l\add*omkakhe laye uyamdumisa:
\v 29 Manengi amadodakazi enze ngenkuthalo, kodwa wena wenyukile phezu kwawo wonke\x + 12.4. 31.10.\x*.
\v 30 Ubuhle buyinkohliso, lokubukeka kuyize; owesifazana owesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* yena uzadunyiswa\x + 11.16.\x*.
\v 31 Mnikeni okuvela esithelweni sezandla zakhe, lemisebenzi yakhe kayimdumise emasangweni.